## Network Types (by geographic scope)

| Type | Description | Example |
|---|---|---|
| **LAN** (Local Area Network) | Small area (office, home, campus); single organization | Home Wi-Fi network |
| **WAN** (Wide Area Network) | Large area — cities, countries, continents; internet is the largest WAN | Multinational corporate network |
| **MAN** (Metropolitan Area Network) | Covers a city/large campus; bigger than LAN, smaller than WAN | — |
| **PAN** (Personal Area Network) | Interconnects devices within a person's immediate workspace (a few meters) | Bluetooth devices connecting to your phone |

