## Common Mistakes & Troubleshooting

| Issue | Fix |
|---|---|
| **IP Address Conflict** (two devices, same IP) | Use DHCP for automatic IPs; verify static IPs are unique |
| **Incorrect Subnet Mask** | Verify consistency across devices (commonly `255.255.255.0` at home) |
| **"No Internet Access"** | Ping default gateway first (local issue if unreachable); then check router's internet connection & DNS |
| **Slow Performance** | Use `ping` to test latency; check router status; consider hardware/plan upgrade |

